title: SEC to Dismiss Winklevoss’ Gemini Crypto Lending Lawsuit
description: The US Securities and Exchange Commission will drop the agency’s 2023 lawsuit against Gemini Trust Co. that accused the firm of illegally raising billions of dollars through an unregistered crypto lending program.
content: The US Securities and Exchange Commission will drop the agency’s 2023 lawsuit against Gemini Trust Co. that accused the firm of illegally raising billions of dollars through an unregistered crypto lending program.
